<body>
<table-wrap>
  <table>
    <colgroup>
      <col width="100%" />
    </colgroup>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>“Bone Remodeling: Akeema Hamlin</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>## Why is Bones Remodeling Important</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>- Repairs damaged bone - Maintains bone strength - Helps
        regulate calcium levels in the blood</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</table-wrap>
<sec id="cells-involved-in-bone-remodeling">
  <title>Cells Involved in bone Remodeling</title>
  <list list-type="bullet">
    <list-item>
      <p>Osteoclasts -&gt; break down old bone</p>
    </list-item>
    <list-item>
      <p>Osteoblasts -&gt; build new bone</p>
    </list-item>
    <list-item>
      <p>Osteocytes -&gt; maintain bone tissue</p>
    </list-item>
  </list>
</sec>
<sec id="bone-remodeling-process">
  <title>Bone Remodeling Process</title>
  <p>1 .Activation - remodeling begins</p>
  <p>2. Resorption - osteoblasts break down bone</p>
</sec>
<sec id="calcium-and-bone-remodeling">
  <title>Calcium and Bone Remodeling</title>
  <list list-type="bullet">
    <list-item>
      <p>Bone store calcium</p>
    </list-item>
    <list-item>
      <p>When the body needs calcium, bone is broken down</p>
    </list-item>
    <list-item>
      <p>Calcium is released into the bloodstream</p>
    </list-item>
  </list>
</sec>
<sec id="factors-that-affect-bone-remodeling">
  <title>Factors That Affect Bone Remodeling</title>
  <list list-type="bullet">
    <list-item>
      <p>Age</p>
    </list-item>
    <list-item>
      <p>Diet (calcium and vitamin D)</p>
    </list-item>
    <list-item>
      <p>Physical activity</p>
    </list-item>
    <list-item>
      <p>Hormones</p>
    </list-item>
  </list>
</sec>
<sec id="bone-remodeling-and-health">
  <title>Bone Remodeling and Health</title>
  <list list-type="bullet">
    <list-item>
      <p>Imbalance can cause bone diseases</p>
    </list-item>
    <list-item>
      <p>Example : Osteoporosis (bones become weak and fragile)</p>
    </list-item>
  </list>
  <sec id="conclusion">
    <title>Conclusion</title>
    <list list-type="bullet">
      <list-item>
        <p>Bone remodeling is essential for maintaining healthy
        bones</p>
      </list-item>
      <list-item>
        <p>It keeps bones strong and supports overall body function</p>
      </list-item>
    </list>
    <p>(<xref alt="Knuth 1984" rid="ref-knuth84" ref-type="bibr">Knuth
    1984</xref>).</p>
  </sec>
</sec>
